description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Elliptical Machine Beginner Workout | Low Impact Interval Training | Fitscope Studio' from the channel Fitscope.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Elliptical Machine Beginner Workout | Low Impact Interval Training | Fitscope Studio

In this low impact interval workout, Brinn makes full use of inclines and resistance on the elliptical machine, all to classic 60s hits.  Great for seniors or anyone wanting a recovery workout easy on the knees.
